# Project conventions

Follow `docs/guidelines/coding.md`. Keep changes consistent with `categories` / `products`.

## Must

- **Plural names** for module folders, files, classes, routes, `.endpoint.http`
- **Response DTOs** on service return types (`*ResponseDto`); input DTOs with validators
- **Error handling**: `NotFoundException` when missing; no fake null-checks on `create` / `findMany`
- **Thin controllers**; Prisma only in services via `PrismaService`
- Use `@/` and `@generated/` imports

## Module shape

`src/modules/<plural>/` with module, controller, service, `dto/` barrel, `<plural>.endpoint.http`. Register in `AppModule`.

## Do not

- Singular module names (`category.service.ts`)
- `BadRequestException` for "not found"
- New architectural layers (repos, CQRS) unless asked
